# Medina Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values.

## Transcription
# Medina transcribes materialized audio chunks via the OSTT CLI (https://ostt.ai/).
# Configure OSTT itself for local models or remote transcription providers.
OSTT_COMMAND=ostt
# OSTT_MODEL=whisper/turbo
# Optional comma-separated extra args appended after `ostt transcribe <chunk>`.
# OSTT_TRANSCRIBE_ARGS=--model,whisper/turbo

## Other AI Services
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key_here
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_key_here
# Or Openrouter?

## Storage Configuration
# Required only by the default streams.ts template. Custom streams.ts deployments may source buckets however they want.
S3_BUCKET=your-bucket-name
# S3_ENDPOINT=https://your-s3-compatible-endpoint.example
# S3_REGION=auto
S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your-access-key
S3_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your-secret-key
# S3_SESSION_TOKEN=your-session-token
# S3_FORCE_PATH_STYLE=true

## Required by the default streams.ts template
# Custom streams.ts deployments may define stream hosts/users directly.
# MEDINA_ROOT is the expected public base URL/host. Requests for other hosts are rejected.
MEDINA_ROOT=http://localhost:3002
# Defaults to default when omitted.
# MEDINA_USERNAME=default
# Credentials identify ways to validate this user. Zero or more are allowed.
# MEDINA_EMAILS=you@example.com
# MEDINA_PHONES=+15555550123
# MEDINA_TAILSCALE_IDS=you@example.com
# Defaults to /default-profile.jpg when omitted.
# MEDINA_PROFILE_PIC_URL=https://example.com/avatar.jpg

## Authorization
MEDINA_TOKEN=replace-with-a-long-random-secret

## Google Drive Connection (optional)
# Enables the in-app Google Drive sync. Create an OAuth client at
# https://console.cloud.google.com/ (Web application type) and add
# https://<your-medina-host>/connect/google/callback as an authorized
# redirect URI. A tailnet-only host works: the redirect is browser-side and
# the only server-to-server call (token exchange) is outbound.
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-google-client-secret

## Optional Overrides
# HOST=127.0.0.1
# PORT=3002
# EXPO_DEV_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:8081
# MEDINA_WORKER_ID=hostname:worker
# INGEST_WORK_LEASE_MS=21600000
